1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. Nc3 Nf6 6. Bf4 e6 7. e3 Be7 8. Bd3
O-O 9. Rc1 Bd7 10. h3 Qb6 11. Qe2 Rfc8 12. O-O Nb4 13. Bb1 Be8 14. Ne5 Nd7 15.
